        <akn:num>2-355.02</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Cost-reimbursement contracts.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_2-355_02_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A cost-reimbursement contract shall not be awarded pursuant to ยง 2-354.02, ยง 2-354.03, or ยง 2-354.04 unless there is a determination and findings that:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_2-355_02_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>All cost-reimbursement contracts shall contain a provision that only costs determined in writing to be reimbursable by the contracting officer, in accordance with cost principles set forth in rules issued pursuant to this chapter, shall be reimbursable.</akn:p></akn:content>
